ActAn Act to amend the Judges Act and certain other Acts in relation to courts
SubjectOrder Fixing April 4, 2008 as the Date of the Coming into Force of subsections 9(1) and (2) of the Judges Act
PrecisOrder fixing April 4, 2008 as the day on which subsections 9(1) and (2) of AN ACT TO AMEND THE JUDGES ACT AND CERTAIN OTHER ACTS IN RELATION TO COURTS, assented to on December 14, 2006, being Chapter 11 of the Statutes of Canada 2006, COME INTO FORCE.
